Slowly living the smol dream as a self-taught designer - something I never thought would have been possible when I was younger (I only thought I‚Äôd be famous after death like Van Gogh and the gang lol)

But seeing so many up-and-coming as well as established artists in Singapore today has definitely been an eye-opener and inspiration to me! Levelling up in the local scene to me has got to be the breaking down of expectations of what a career is or has to be, especially in the creative industry - be it arts, music, etc.

Forever Faster, Stronger, Better Together with my #PUMASG +65 Crew @minhuahahaha @jeremykieran @song_uiyoung @timotheeyjw @toshrock

So ecstatic to be part of this creative community, as we celebrate the launch of PUMA‚Äôs flagship store! The new PUMA 313@somerset flagship store is now open, head down to check out the new space!

Finally sharing my F1 2022 experience!!! ü§üüèª

Took me a whole week because after Sunday, my camera crashed, my SD card crashed... And I crashed HAHAHA.

Not even kidding man I took 2 while days to fully recover - totally underestimated the toll that drawing for 2.5 days would take on my tiny body. But wouldn't have traded it for anything else! The last time I attended F1 was at least 5 years ago... But this was definitely one experience I'll never forget. This amazing A-team put together by @smxne, the crazy energy and just talking to all the people who came by and hung out with us, took care of us, and performed for us. Couldn't have done it without this amazing bunch! 

We got some of the best seats in the house by the Wharf Stage too hehe ‚úåüèª till the next one! üî•
